						<a href="#SUB1">After Japan's decision not to raise interest rates, traders are expecting the Fed to keep any increases low.</a><p>
						<img src="/imgs/wee-page.gif" align=left>
						<a href="#SUB2">Globally, U.S. stocks are attractive.</a><p>
						<img src="/imgs/wee-page.gif" align=left>
						<a href="#SUB3">In Japan. share prices have been stimulated by the highest first-quarter GDP in two decades.</a><p>
