</font>						<a href="#NASD:FORE">FORE Systems, Inc.</a><br>

						<a href="#NYSE:SGI">Silicon Graphics, Inc.</a><br>

						<a href="#NYSE:CA">Computer Associates International, Inc.</a><br>

