<DOCOLDNO>IA030-000640-B014-319</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.worth.com:80/articles/Z9310O04.html 204.141.48.165 19970209082539 text/html 12183
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Sun, 09 Feb 1997 08:26:28 GMT
Server: Apache/1.1.0
