						Spring cleaning means airing out cabinets, which we've done for federal cabinet departments. Here's a tally of employee tax debtors and the average tab per head: Agriculture, 4,669 ($3,900); Commerce, 1,863 ($5,802); Defense (civilian), 45,345 ($4,703); Education, 340 ($7,403); Energy, 773 ($7,690); Health and Human Services, 3,517 ($5,055); HUD, 833 ($5,002); Interior, 3,633 ($4,336); Justice, 3,906 ($3,035); Labor, 991 ($5,240); State, 790 ($3,951); Transportation, 2,663 ($6,778); Treasury, 5,399 ($3,182); and Veterans Affairs, 16,991 ($5,376).<p><p><p><p>

