		<title> Worth OnLine - 96/03-Green Magic</title>
	</head>
	
	<body background="/imgs/goldbarsmooth.gif" bgcolor="#FFFFFF"
	      text="#000000" link="#FF0000" vlink="#BB0000"> 	
	<a name="#top">
	<table width=550 cellpadding=10 cellspacing=5>
	
	<tr>
		<td width=390 valign=top> 
		
		<a href=/cgi/ad-relay.cgi?http://www.pcfn.com/6015.html?worth+PCFN16.gif+Archives>
<img src="/ads/PCFN16.gif" border=3 width=372 height=45 alt="PC Financial Network"></a>


		</td>
		<td  width=150>
		<!-- empty cell -->
		</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
	<td width=390 valign=top>
		
		<center>
		<p>
		<b><a href="/index.html">Home</a>  |  <a href="/departments/departments.html">Departments</a>  |  <a href="/search/query.html">Search</a>  |  <a href="/forums/index.html">Message Boards</a></b>
		<pre>
		</pre>
				<font size=5><b>Green Magic</b></font><br>
				<font size=6><b>96/03-Green Magic</b></font><br>
				<font size=4></font><p>
				</center>
				
				<blockquote>
					<center>
						<font size=4><b><i></i></b></font><p>
					</center>
					<font size=4>
						March 1996
Worth magazine/Outfront<p>GREEN MAGIC<p>By Melissa Jeffries<p>Barrie Dolnick, a former ad executive turned mystic (and a Gemini), has written Simple Spells for Success (Crown), which will "bring positive results to any endeavor." <p>Dolnick's New York firm, Executive Mystic, sells this otherwordly advantage to businesspeople, for whom she has concocted spells and "Power Bundles" to attract investors and deals. She also provides tarot-card business projections. <p>Dolnick offers Worth readers this spell to attract money:<p>On a Friday during a waxing moon and in the second hour after sunset, light a green candle. Place yellow roses in a vase with water. Dab one of the following scents on the candle: poppy, honeysuckle, or almond. Place a bunch of grapes next to the candle.<p>Say aloud: I draw in the eternal flow of prosperity to connect with me on this Venus evening. I call in fire, earth, air, and water to manifest abundance around me. I affirm I am open to all forms of prosperity, and that it comes to me easily and readily. I ask that I be guided to use this gift within the greater good. <p>So be it. And so it is.<p>Blow out the candle. Eat at least one grape. Repeat as desired during any waxing moon. <p><p><p>
KEYWORDS: Entertainment Industry

					</font>
					<p>
		
		
		
