Worth magazine/Outfront<p>GLOBAL CHIC
A checklist of cool for status seekers in Montreal.<p>
-> Being the inspiration for a Leonard Cohen song.<p>-> Smoking smuggled Marlboros at the Shed Cafe.<p>-> Displaying an autographed photo of reclusive writer Rejean Ducharme -- discreetly, of course.<p>-> Knowing your car mechanic's home phone number.<p>-> Grabbing a bite on the Ritz patio, hair still wet from an early-morning dip at Le Sanctuaire.<p>-> Jumping the line at Le Dogue.<p>-> Having Mordecai Richler buy you a drink at Grumpy's.<p>-> Getting a credit card from Ogilvy -- but only so you're on all the society mailing lists.<p><p><p><p>

