Which tobacco deal glows brightest?<p>Cigarettes may ruin your health, but they can help your wardrobe -- if you don't mind advertising your addiction, that is. We comparison-shopped among three popular brands' frequent-smoker plans.<p>              CAMEL          MARLBORO       WINSTON
