				<font size=5><b>Global Chic</b></font><br>
				<font size=6><b>94/10-Global Chic</b></font><br>
				<font size=4></font><p>
				</center>
				
				<blockquote>
					<center>
						<font size=4><b><i></i></b></font><p>
					</center>
					<font size=4>
						October 1994
Worth magazine/Outfront<p>GLOBAL CHIC
A checklist of cool for  status seekers in Oslo.<p>-> Making it with one of the crew members in King Harald's wooden eight-meter.<p>-> Getting into the philosophy of "Sofie's Verden," a popular children's book.<p>-> Being a "3-H" member -- you ski at Hemsedal, sunbathe topless at Huk Beach, dine at Herregardskroa.<p>-> Breaking bread with artist Odd Nerdrum and his disciples.<p>-> Sending your kids for a year abroad in Australia.<p>-> Hanging with Earle Hyman, who played Russell Huxtable on "The Cosby Show."<p>-> Serving alcohol after 12:30 a.m. at an illegal warehouse party.<p><p><p>

					</font>
