A checklist of cool for status seekers in Prague<p>Getting married in Staromestske Namest (Old Town Square) and departing in a horse-drawn carriage<p>Brushing your teeth with Evian water<p>Returning the economy minister's tennis balls from the next court over at the Hotel Atrium<p>Serving a really good lasagna to your dinner guests<p>Partying with the members of the Velvet Revival Band<p>Reading from your novel in progress at the Royalist Club, an exclusive beer hall in the basement of a medieval building<p>Driving a truly old Skoda automobile--particularly a model from the 1930s<p>Buying Vaclav Havel a beer at his latest hangout<p>

