<html>
	<head>
		<title> Worth OnLine - 94/01-Global Chic</title>
	</head>
	
	<body background="/imgs/goldbarsmooth.gif" bgcolor="#FFFFFF"
	      text="#000000" link="#FF0000" vlink="#BB0000"> 	
	<a name="#top">
	<table width=550 cellpadding=10 cellspacing=5>
	
	<tr>
		<td width=390 valign=top> 
		
		<a href=/cgi/ad-relay.cgi?http://www.pcfn.com/6007.html?worth+PCFN25.gif+Archives>
<img src="/ads/PCFN25.gif" border=3 width=372 height=45 alt="PC Financial Network"></a>


		</td>
		<td  width=150>
		<!-- empty cell -->
		</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
	<td width=390 valign=top>
		
		<center>
		<p>
		<b><a href="/index.html">Home</a>  |  <a href="/departments/departments.html">Departments</a>  |  <a href="/search/query.html">Search</a>  |  <a href="/forums/index.html">Message Boards</a></b>
		<pre>
		</pre>
				<font size=5><b> </b></font><br>
				<font size=6><b>94/01-Global Chic</b></font><br>
				<font size=4></font><p>
				</center>
				
				<blockquote>
					<center>
						<font size=4><b><i></i></b></font><p>
					</center>
					<font size=4>
						 
A checklist of cool for status seekers in Caracas<p>--Flying a private plane to Los Roques, a group of coral islands, to buy prawns<p>--Checking your cellular phone at the door of Primi, a hot restaurant in the Castellana district<p>--Dating a Miss Venezuela pageant winner or runner-up<p>--Sending the kids to summer camp in New England<p>--Having a nanny who speaks Spanish and English<p>--Swapping coup rumors over Chivas and morcillas (blood sausages) at La Estancia, an Argentine-style grill
 <p><p>

					</font>
					<p>
		
		
		
