Beverly Loan Co., oldest pawn shop in Beverly Hills, California<p>
1.  Diamond ring 
2.  Rolex watch
3.  Cartier watch
4.  Diamond tennis bracelet
5.  Dunhill or Cartier cigarette lighter
6.  Cartier clock
