<html>
	<head>
		<title> Worth OnLine - 93/11-My Three Sons</title>
	</head>
	
	<body background="/imgs/goldbarsmooth.gif" bgcolor="#FFFFFF"
	      text="#000000" link="#FF0000" vlink="#BB0000"> 	
	<a name="#top">
	<table width=550 cellpadding=10 cellspacing=5>
	
	<tr>
		<td width=390 valign=top> 
		
		<a href=/cgi/ad-relay.cgi?http://www.pcfn.com/6015.html?worth+PCFN16.gif+Archives>
<img src="/ads/PCFN16.gif" border=3 width=372 height=45 alt="PC Financial Network"></a>


		</td>
		<td  width=150>
		<!-- empty cell -->
		</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
	<td width=390 valign=top>
		
		<center>
		<p>
		<b><a href="/index.html">Home</a>  |  <a href="/departments/departments.html">Departments</a>  |  <a href="/search/query.html">Search</a>  |  <a href="/forums/index.html">Message Boards</a></b>
		<pre>
		</pre>
				<font size=5><b></b></font><br>
				<font size=6><b>93/11-My Three Sons</b></font><br>
				<font size=4></font><p>
				</center>
				
				<blockquote>
					<center>
						<font size=4><b><i></i></b></font><p>
					</center>
					<font size=4>
						
A dynasty is born<p>Sirio Maccioni, owner of Le Cirque, New York's venerable four-star restaurant, is tuning in to changing times. By the end of 1994, he plans to set up his three sons in a less formal establishment. The new place, serving "simple, straight" Italian food at reasonable prices, is seen as a model for other Maccioni restaurants. Eldest son Mario, 28, ultimately will run the new eatery by himself, while Marco, 25, will likely run a version in Paris and Mauro, 21, may get his own spin-off in Milan. Maccioni has also been exploring his dream of running a hotel in his native Italy; wife Egiis toying with a fast-food idea. Why all the activity? In part, Maccioni is ensuring a legacy:"I am very close to 60, and that bothers me very much." But he also knows that another Le Cirque isn't viable in the frugal '90s. Plus, it would spoil his sons:"You don't buy a Ferrari as a first car."<p><p>
KEYWORDS: Family Business
					</font>
					<p>
		
		
		
</td><td width=150 valign=top>

<center>
		
	<a href="/index.html">
	<IMG SRC="/imgs/datalineyellow.gif" border=0 alt="Worth"></a><p>
</center>
<pre>


</pre>
					<tt><font size=+1>
					<center>
						<img src="/imgs/1page.gif"><br>About 1 page

					</font>
					</tt>
					</center>

					<pre>
					</pre>


					</font>
					<p>

