						Last year audiophiles spent millions on high-end speaker cable, including some that's sold in velvet-lined boxes. Insane?Probably:Tests say spending more than $20 on wire doesn't make sense, and some experts call high-end cable an outright fraud. A shopping list:<p>- Radio Shack "Mega" cable:99 cents a foot<p>- Monster M.75 cable:$5 a foot<p>- Cardas Quadlink-Five cable:$33.67 a foot<p>- AudioQuest Dragon cable:$150 a foot<p>- Kimber Kable Model 88 cable:$1,875 a foot<p><p>

