					</pre>


					</font>
					<p>

<font size=+1><b>Company Index</b><br>
</font>						<a href="#NYSE:MO">Philip Morris Companies Inc.</a><br>

						<a href="#NYSE:MRK">Merck & Co., Inc.</a><br>

						<a href="#NYSE:IBM">International Business Machines Corporation</a><br>

					<p>

<font size=+1><b>Mutual Fund Index</b><br>
</font>						<a href="#FUND:AHERX">American Heritage Fund</a><br>

