USAA Tax-Exempt Short-Term, 800-382-8722, 4.27, 4.30<BR>
Vanguard Muni. Limited-Term, 800-662-7447, 4.07, 4.20<BR>
Dreyfus Short-Intermd. Muni. Bond, 800-645-6561, 3.70, 3.63<BR>
Vanguard Municipal Short-Term, 800-662-7447, 3.59, 3.72<BR>
<BR>
Data as of 12/19/96. Source: Lipper Analytical Services.<BR>
<BR><p>
**Investing for a Goal at Least Five Years Away**
Our picks with an emphasis on total return<p>
In the picks below -- suitable for a patient investor able to tolerate sizable near-term dips -- we emphasize five-year total returns and high current yields. We don't ignore safety altogether; top choices must have a demonstrated ability to limit downside risk. Strong Short-Term and Fidelity Mortgage, in fact, place extra emphasis on safety (they are meant to appeal to savers) but have still achieved impressive five-year returns. Northeast Investors Trust employs a different approach. It ventures into lower-quality bonds than many other junk funds -- seeking high returns -- and counts on managers Ernest and Bruce Monrad's due diligence to limit risk.  
<BR>
TAXABLE<BR>
Northeast Investors Trust, 800-225-6704, 8.69%, 15.57%<BR>
Vanguard Fixed-Income GNMA, 800-662-7447, 7.10, 7.04<BR>
Strong Short-Term Bond, 800-368-1030, 6.90, 6.73<BR>
Fidelity Mortgage Securities, 800-544-8888, 6.52, 7.40<BR>
Dreyfus Basic GNMA, 800-645-6561, 6.15, 7.57<BR>
<BR>
TAX-FREE<BR>
