Sit Tax-Free Income, 800-332-5580, 5.50, 7.20<BR>
Vanguard Municipal High-Yield, 800-662-7447, 5.47, 8.06<BR>
USAA Tax-Exempt Intermd.-Term, 800-382-8722, 5.14, 7.04<BR>
Vanguard Municipal Intermd.-Term, 800-338-2550, 4.58, 7.32<BR>
